  ],
  "cards": [
    {
      "id": "intro-0",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "简介",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "这个 APT 快速参考备忘单显示了它的常用命令使用清单。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-1",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "介绍",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "APT（`A`dvanced `P`ackaging `T`ools）是`Debian`及其派生的`Linux`软件包管理器。APT可以自动下载，配置，安装二进制或者源代码格式的软件包，因此简化了Unix系统上管理软件的过程。APT最早被设计成`dpkg的前端`，用来处理deb格式的软件包。现在经过`APT-RPM`组织修改，APT已经可以安装在支持RPM的系统管理RPM包。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-2",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "它结合了apt-get和apt-cache工具中最常用的命令以及选项与默认值。`apt`命令必须以具有`sudo`权限的用户运行。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-3",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "命令语法格式"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-4",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ apt [ OPTIONS ] COMMAND"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-5",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "相关参考文献"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-6",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "• [APT（8） 官方网站](https://manpages.debian.org/unstable/apt/apt.8.en.html)\n• [apt.conf(5) 官方文档](https://manpages.debian.org/unstable/apt/apt.conf.5.en.html)\n• [sources.list(5) 官方文档](https://manpages.debian.org/unstable/apt/sources.list.5.en.html)"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-7",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "命令查询",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "子命令描述和任务，显示 apt 命令和选项。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-8",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ apt -h or --help\n# 或\n$ apt"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-9",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "查看指令用法"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-10",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ man apt"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-11",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "update",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "从APT存储库中获取最新索引数据。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-12",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt update"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-13",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "在升级或安装新软件包之前，建议始终先运行一次更新软件包索引。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-14",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "upgrade",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "将安装的软件包升级到最新版本，该命令不会升级那些已删除软件包的依赖。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-15",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt upgrade"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-16",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "升级单个软件包。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-17",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt upgrade package_name"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-18",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "升级整个系统，则会删除当前安装的软件包。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-19",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt full-upgrade"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-20",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "install",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "安装软件包。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-21",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt install package_name"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-22",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "如果只想升级，不要安装"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-23",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt install <package_name> --only-upgrade"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-24",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "安装多个软件包，包名用空格分隔。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-25",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt install package1 package2"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-26",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "安装本地deb文件，提供文件的完整路径。否则，apt命令将尝试从APT存储库中检索并安装软件包。\n`Deb是所有基于Debian的发行版使用的安装软件包格式`。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-27",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt install /full/path/file.deb"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-28",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "remove和purge",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "要删除已安装的程序包，你可以使用apt子命令`remove`和`purge`。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-29",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "remove",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "remove子命令将卸载指定的软件包，`但可能会留下一些配置文件`。\n通过remove方式卸载的软件包可以通过重新安装软件包来恢复，因为个人配置文件还在本地。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-30",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "卸载指定的软件包"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-31",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt remove package_name"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-32",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "指定多个软件包，以空格分隔"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-33",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt remove package1 package2"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-34",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "purge",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "purge子命令将卸载指定的软件包和配置文件。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-35",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt purge package_name"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-36",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "autoremove自动删除依赖",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "用于删除自动安装的包，这些包都是为了满足其他包的依赖关系，现在不再需要这些包，因为依赖关系已更改或者同时删除了需要它们的包。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-37",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt autoremove"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-38",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "list",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "打印所有软件包的列表，包括软件包的版本和结构的信息。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-39",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt list"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-40",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "要确定是否安装了指定的软件包，可以使用grep命令过滤输出。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-41",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt list | grep package_name"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-42",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "仅列出已安装的软件包。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-43",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt list --installed"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-44",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "获取可升级软件包的列表。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-45",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt list --upgradeable"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-46",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "搜索查找软件包详细信息 - search",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "在可用软件源列表中搜索指定的软件包。如果找到该软件包，则将返回名称与搜索词匹配的软件包。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-47",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt search package_name"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-48",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "show",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "显示有关给定软件包的信息，包括其依赖项、安装、下载大小、软件包可用的来源、软件包内容的描述等。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-49",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt show package_name"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-50",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "edit-sources 快速换源",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "允许您在首选的文本编辑器中编辑`sources.list(5)` 文件，同时还提供基本的健全性检查。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-51",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "首次换源可以使用`edit-sources`"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-52",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt show edit-sources"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-53",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "换源后更新一下软件包索引。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-54",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo apt update"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-55",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "之后可以使用`select-editor`更换默认编辑器"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-56",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "bash",
      "code": "$ sudo select-editor"
    }
  ],
